{
  "stem": "24259.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was late summer then, so the-- the-- the wheat was quite high.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Or corn, I don't remember exactly what it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were able to hide in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this was during the night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my mother and my aunt remained in a hole.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But through some miracle, my mother was able to get herself out of the hole with my aunt, and they, too, escaped out of the barn.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And eventually we met up in the area of the-- of the fields.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were reunited.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I do remember personally being out during the night and seeing these balls of fire overhead just going across.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I-- I don't recall.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It might have been shooting, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But I remember seeing these balls of fire going overhead.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "During that time, even though it was German-occupied, the Polish residents and the Ukrainian residents used to have, like, little civil wars between them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I believe the Ukrainian set the barn on the fire during that time, I'm told, or I've overheard my parents discuss it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The last name was Sharek, S-H-A-R-E-K.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I believe that's the way he would have spelled the name.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was a Polish farmer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Late, late summer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Possibly early fall.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we hid out in-- in the fields and in the woods during that time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father, again, was forced to contact various gentile farmer friends of his, people that he knew over the years, to see if they would take us in as well.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And after a period of a few weeks, I guess, just hiding out in the-- in the woods and in the fields, my father was perhaps able to persuade another farmer.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This time, I believe he was of Ukrainian descent.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he-- he was willing to take us in.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
